 <!-- Page Content -->
    
    <div class="container">

      <div class="row">

        <!-- Post Content Column -->
        <div class="col-md-8">

          <!-- Title -->
          <h1 class="mt-4">{{post.title}}</h1>

          <!-- Author -->
          <p class="lead">
            by
            <a href="#">Tony Atuoha</a>
          </p>

          <hr>

          <!-- Date/Time -->
          <p>Posted on {{generate_date post.date 'MMM Do YYYY'}}</p>

          <hr>

          <!-- Preview Image -->
          <img class="img-fluid rounded" src="/uploads/{{post.file}}" alt="">

          <hr>

          <!-- Post Content -->
          <p class="lead">{{post.sub}}</p>


          <blockquote class="blockquote">
            <p class="mb-0">Each day wake up and ask yourself what will make you feel most alive that day</p>
            <footer class="blockquote-footer">Crafted from 
              <cite title="Source Title">Chrome Momentum Extension</cite>
            </footer>
          </blockquote>

          <p>{{post.body}}</p>

         

          <hr>

          <!-- Comments Form -->
          <div class="card my-4">
            <h5 class="card-header">Leave a Comment:</h5>
            <div class="card-body">
              <form>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <textarea class="form-control" rows="3"></textarea>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Single Comment -->
         <div class="media mb-4">
                <img class="d-flex mr-3 rounded-circle" width="50" src="/uploads/default.png" alt="">
                <div class="media-body">
                    <h5 class="mt-0">John Phils </h5>
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Ex atque numquam reprehenderit quod facere expedita asperiores fuga quia non voluptatum sed distinctio, natus, repellendus dolor dolorum modi mollitia, explicabo officiis..

                    <div class="media mt-4">
                        <img class="d-flex mr-3 rounded-circle" width="50" src="/uploads/default.png" alt="">
                        <div class="media-body">
                        <h5 class="mt-0">Sandra Mattiews</h5>
                        Cras sit amet nibh libero, in gravida nulla. Nulla vel metus scelerisque ante sollicitudin. Cras purus odio, vestibulum in vulputate at, tempus viverra turpis. Fusce condimentum nunc ac nisi vulputate fringilla. Donec lacinia congue felis in faucibus.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        {{> home/sidebar}}

        </div>
      <!-- /.row -->

    </div>
    <!-- /.container -->